						               													<description>In Operation Basterds your objective is to rescue prisoners from a concentration camp where you will go through different phases or areas of the game such as the jungle or the airport, where your machine gun will be your best weapon that can lead you to victory, as well as dodging obstacles in the jungle. Several games in one that will make you feel the emotion of one of the best shooters of the 80s.&amp;#10;A game to be played in solitaire mode or up to 5 players, in which you roll all the dice on your mission sheet. Choose and shoot all the dice on a zone of operations between MAP, ENGAGEMENT, AIR STRIKE AND PRISONERS. Soldier remember, each die you roll off the game sheet will be counted as wounds! For each wound you will lose one die for future throws, if you lose your six dice it is GAME OVER.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
